{"tid":1682884,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"大小便要申請嗎？ - 高慧然","createTime":"2019-10-30T10:26:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T10:29:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f57cb527b954764b5b1275f22219dbed40090d54","tid":1682884,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T10:26:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20191030/20796132/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191030%2F20796132%2F&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt30uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=740d6a19\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191030%2F20796132%2F&h=ea3c1f8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20191030/20796132/</a><br />\n<br />\n大小便要申請嗎？ - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191030/large/1572334211_430b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191030%2Flarge%2F1572334211_430b.jpg&h=b0f898b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有傳香港警察聯絡「香港長跑網」負責人，提醒該會練跑及跑後聚餐均須提前七日以書面方式知會警務處處長，並詳細列出時間、路線等細則。該會負責人附上警察牌照課發出的電郵截圖並告知傳媒。<br />\n<br />\n消息雖荒謬，但柒婆治下，香港人連戴口罩的權利都被剝奪，那麼，被進一步剝奪人身自由並非不可能的事。似乎任何涉及眾數的人類活動，都有可能被冠上非法集結的罪名，從而被打壓、被禁止。<br />\n<br />\n幾年前，我在香港有一群打網球的朋友，人數超過十個。我們每星期兩次，包起三、四個網球場，定期打網球。打完球，一大班人浩浩蕩蕩去飲酒打邊爐。不知道這群波友現在還有沒有繼續打球？若是，需不需要向警方申請不反對通知書？一群穿着運動服和運動鞋、揹着網球拍的人在街頭走過，會不會被控非法集結及持有攻擊性武器呢？不過是幾年時間，我們曾經的生活日常，竟然變得遙不可及。<br />\n<br />\n去年，看到北京為了迎國慶，規定民眾使用公廁必須提供身分證及手機號碼做實名登記，記錄大便還是小便、如廁時間等等，若在廁所時間過長，必須寫一份200字以上的說明，我們深感詫異，以為在看周星星電影。但此刻再看到這段舊聞，只覺毛骨悚然。我們距離大小便登記的日子還遠嗎？ <br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk"},{"pid":"15e1e73dcea7149a4a93c6f105108ec31fe99afe","tid":1682884,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T10:26:58.000Z","msg":"已經有13個英美參議員/單位就GPhone出聲<br />\n快啲Rt and like and reply哂佢<br />\n全部響哂<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> /Task1</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt30uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=929d78dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a>"},{"pid":"d01c7a8a602ecddc3b5d76002bbf24fe2e395f40","tid":1682884,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T10:29:21.000Z","msg":"同昔日交通迷討論區異曲同工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}